                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8086" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0371</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1712 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青蓝携手,薪火相传:京博恒丰如何破解师父“留一手”?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Qinglan Hand in Hand, Inheritance of Flame: How can Jingbo Hengfeng crack the mentor&#39;s &quot;Hold back a trick or two&quot;?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曾颢，余薇，罗焰，于静，万刚华，白坤，曹淑兵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西科技师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东京博控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">京博恒丰；师徒制；“留一手”；指导动机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jingbo hengfeng; Mentoring; Hold back a trick or two;Mentor motives</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">师徒制作为企业人力资源管理与开发的重要工具,对促进员工的成长与发展具有积极作用。本案例以京博控股集团恒丰分公司白坤总经理的三次会议破解师父“留一手”难题为主线，描述了京博恒丰从粗放式、放养式到精细化、制度化的师徒制管理方式沿革过程，通过将师带徒与职级并行制度和勋章等级制度等密切结合起来，激发师带徒的热情和责任，提升师父指导动机的过程。本案例旨在引导学生分析京博恒丰破解师徒制“留一手”难题的实践，理解师徒制中师父指导行为的形成过程，认识指导动机的作用及类型，并运用ERG理论揭示师带徒方案优化的原因，为企业师徒制管理实践提供指导。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As an important tool for human resource management and development in enterprises, mentorship plays a positive role in promoting the growth and development of employees.  This case focuses on three meetings of General Manager Bai Kun of Shandong Jingbo Hengfeng Branch to solve the problem of &quot;hold back a trick or two&quot; for the mentor, Hold back a trick or two&quot;. It describes the evolution of Jingbo Hengfeng&#39;s mentoring management from extensive and free range to refined and institutionalized. By closely combining the mentoring system with the rank parallel system and the medal level system, it stimulates the enthusiasm and responsibility of the mentor, and enhances the mentor motives. This case aims to guide students through analyzing the practice of Jingbo Hengfeng in solving the problem of &quot;hold back a trick or two&quot; in the mentoring, focusing on  the formation process of mentoring behavior in the mentoring system, and realizing the role and types of  mentor motives, using ERG theory to reveal the reasons for optimizing the mentoring, and providing reference for the management practice of enterprise mentoring.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">需要-动机-行为的关系；指导动机的概念及类型；ERG理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
